    <p>You can perform a package
      upgrade for Ubuntu/Debian Linux by installing the updated <codeph>.pkg</codeph>
      package:</p>
    
    <codeblock>
 &gt; sudo dpkg -i couchbase-server-architecture___meta_current_release.deb
</codeblock>
    
   
    
